"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe value of <code>upload_max_filesize</code> in your <code>PHP.ini</code> needs be set to at least the desired limit.\n"
"\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tCurrently <code>upload_max_filesize</code> is set to %s (%s byte)"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:506
msgid "Register policy"
msgstr "注册政策"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:507
msgid "Maximum Users"
msgstr "最大用户数"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:507
msgid ""
"If defined, the register policy is automatically closed when the given "
"number of users is reached and reopens the registry when the number drops "
"below the limit. It only works when the policy is set to open or close, but "
"not when the policy is set to approval."
msgstr "如果启用，当达到指定用户数量时会自动关闭注册，并在数量低于限制的数量时重新开放注册。它仅在设置为开放注册或关闭注册时才有效，而在设置为批准注册时无效。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:508
msgid "Maximum Daily Registrations"
msgstr "每日最大注册量"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:508
msgid ""
"If registration is permitted above, this sets the maximum number of new user"
" registrations to accept per day.  If register is set to closed, this "
"setting has no effect."
msgstr "如果上面允许注册，将设置每天接受的新用户注册的最大数量。如果关闭注册，则此设置无效。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:509
msgid "Register text"
msgstr "注册正文"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:509
msgid ""
"Will be displayed prominently on the registration page. You can use BBCode "
"here."
msgstr "将显示在注册页面的显着位置。你可以在这里使用 BBCode。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:510
msgid "Forbidden Nicknames"
msgstr "禁止的昵称"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:510
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of nicknames that are forbidden from registration. "
"Preset is a list of role names according RFC 2142."
msgstr "禁止使用逗号注册昵称。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:511
msgid "Accounts abandoned after x days"
msgstr "几天后抛弃账户"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:511
msgid ""
"Will not waste system resources polling external sites for abandonded "
"accounts. Enter 0 for no time limit."
msgstr "拒绝浪费系统资源看外网站找丢弃的账户。输入0为无时限。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:512
msgid "Allowed friend domains"
msgstr "允许的朋友域"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:512
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of domains which are allowed to establish friendships "
"with this site. Wildcards are accepted. Empty to allow any domains"
msgstr "逗号分隔的域名许根这个网站结友谊。通配符行。空的允许所有的域名。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:513
msgid "Allowed email domains"
msgstr "允许的电子邮件域"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:513
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of domains which are allowed in email addresses for "
"registrations to this site. Wildcards are accepted. Empty to allow any "
"domains"
msgstr "逗号分隔的域名可接受在邮件地址为这网站的注册。通配符行。空的允许所有的域名。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:514
msgid "Disallowed email domains"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:514
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of domains which are rejected as email addresses for "
"registrations to this site. Wildcards are accepted."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:515
msgid "Block public"
msgstr "阻止公开"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:515
msgid ""
"Check to block public access to all otherwise public personal pages on this "
"site unless you are currently logged in."
msgstr "勾选阻止未登录用户访问公开页面。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:516
msgid "Force publish"
msgstr "强行发布"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:516
msgid ""
"Check to force all profiles on this site to be listed in the site directory."
msgstr "选中将站点上的所有用户都列在站点目录中。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:516
msgid "Enabling this may violate privacy laws like the GDPR"
msgstr "启用此项可能会违反隐私法律，譬如 GDPR 等"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:517
msgid "Global directory URL"
msgstr "全局目录 URL"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:517
msgid ""
"URL to the global directory. If this is not set, the global directory is "
"completely unavailable to the application."
msgstr "全局目录的 URL。如果未设置，则全局目录对应用程序完全不可用。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:518
msgid "Private posts by default for new users"
msgstr "新用户默认写私人文章"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:518
msgid ""
"Set default post permissions for all new members to the default privacy "
"circle rather than public."
msgstr "将所有新成员的默认发帖权限设置为隐私而不是公开。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:519
msgid "Don't include post content in email notifications"
msgstr "别包含文章内容在邮件消息"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:519
msgid ""
"Don't include the content of a post/comment/private message/etc. in the "
"email notifications that are sent out from this site, as a privacy measure."
msgstr "不要包含帖子/评论/私人消息/等的内容。在从本网站发出的电子邮件通知中，作为一项隐私措施。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:520
msgid "Disallow public access to addons listed in the apps menu."
msgstr "不允许插件的公众使用权在应用选单。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:520
msgid ""
"Checking this box will restrict addons listed in the apps menu to members "
"only."
msgstr "复选这个框为把应用选内插件限制仅成员"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:521
msgid "Don't embed private images in posts"
msgstr "别嵌入私人图案在文章里"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:521
msgid ""
"Don't replace locally-hosted private photos in posts with an embedded copy "
"of the image. This means that contacts who receive posts containing private "
"photos will have to authenticate and load each image, which may take a "
"while."
msgstr "不要将帖子中本地托管的私人照片替换为嵌入的图像副本。这意味着，收到包含私人照片的帖子的联系人将不得不验证并加载每张图像，这可能需要一段时间。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:522
msgid "Explicit Content"
msgstr "露骨内容"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:522
msgid ""
"Set this to announce that your node is used mostly for explicit content that"
" might not be suited for minors. This information will be published in the "
"node information and might be used, e.g. by the global directory, to filter "
"your node from listings of nodes to join. Additionally a note about this "
"will be shown at the user registration page."
msgstr "设置此选项以通知您的节点主要用于可能不适合未成年人的显式内容。此信息将在节点信息中发布，并且可能被(例如)全局目录用来从要加入的节点列表中过滤您的节点。此外，用户注册页面上将显示有关此问题的说明。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:523
msgid "Only local search"
msgstr "仅限本地搜索"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:523
msgid ""
"Blocks search for users who are not logged in to prevent crawlers from "
"blocking your system."
msgstr "阻止未登录用户搜索，以防止爬虫。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:524
msgid "Blocked tags for trending tags"
msgstr "趋势中屏蔽的标签"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:524
msgid ""
"Comma separated list of hashtags that shouldn't be displayed in the trending"
" tags."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:525
msgid "Cache contact avatars"
msgstr "缓存联系人头像"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:525
msgid ""
"Locally store the avatar pictures of the contacts. This uses a lot of "
"storage space but it increases the performance."
msgstr "存储联系人的头像。这会占用大量存储空间，但会提高性能。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:526
msgid "Allow Users to set remote_self"
msgstr "允许用户用遥远的自身"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:526
msgid ""
"With checking this, every user is allowed to mark every contact as a "
"remote_self in the repair contact dialog. Setting this flag on a contact "
"causes mirroring every posting of that contact in the users stream."
msgstr "选择这个之后，用户们允许表明熟人当遥远的自身在熟人修理页。遥远的自身所有文章被复制到用户文章流。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:527
msgid "Allow Users to set up relay channels"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:527
msgid ""
"If enabled, it is possible to create relay users that are used to reshare "
"content based on user defined channels."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:528
msgid "Adjust the feed poll frequency"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:528
msgid "Automatically detect and set the best feed poll frequency."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:529
msgid "Minimum poll interval"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:529
msgid ""
"Minimal distance in minutes between two polls for mail and feed contacts. "
"Reasonable values are between 1 and 59."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:530
msgid "Enable multiple registrations"
msgstr "启用多人注册"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:530
msgid "Enable users to register additional accounts for use as pages."
msgstr "允许用户注册其他帐户类型以用作页面。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:531
msgid "Enable OpenID"
msgstr "启用OpenID"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:531
msgid "Enable OpenID support for registration and logins."
msgstr "为注册和登录启用 OpenID 支持。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:532
msgid "Enable full name check"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:532
msgid ""
"Prevents users from registering with a display name with fewer than two "
"parts separated by spaces."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:533
msgid "Email administrators on new registration"
msgstr "新注册的电子邮件管理员"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:533
msgid ""
"If enabled and the system is set to an open registration, an email for each "
"new registration is sent to the administrators."
msgstr "如果启用开放注册，则每次新注册都会向管理员发送一封电子邮件。"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:534
msgid "Community pages for visitors"
msgstr "访问者的社区页面"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:534
msgid ""
"Which community pages should be available for visitors. Local users always "
"see both pages."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:535
msgid "Posts per user on community page"
msgstr "个用户文章数量在社会页"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:535
msgid ""
"The maximum number of posts per user on the local community page. This is "
"useful, when a single user floods the local community page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:536
msgid "Posts per server on community page"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:536
msgid ""
"The maximum number of posts per server on the global community page. This is"
" useful, when posts from a single server flood the global community page."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:537
msgid "Display local media to visitors"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:537
msgid ""
"When enabled, locally stored media, such as pictures and videos, will be "
"displayed to visitors who are not logged in. When disabled, a message will "
"appear informing visitors that the media is only available to logged-in "
"users."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:538
msgid "Display remote media to visitors"
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:538
msgid ""
"When enabled, visitors who are not logged in will be able to view non-"
"locally stored media such as pictures and videos. When disabled, visitors "
"will see a message informing them that the media is available on the remote "
"site."
msgstr ""

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:540
msgid "Enable Mail support"
msgstr "启用邮件支持"

#: src/Module/Admin/Site.php:540
msgid ""
